    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it clearly shows its age and mileage. Mechanically, the engine and transmission are functional, but there are some minor fluid seeps that will eventually need attention, and the suspension has lost some of its original firmness. The exterior features several visible scratches, small dings, and some fading paint on the hood. Inside, the upholstery and carpets show significant wear and some staining, though all essential electronics remain operational. It is a practical option for someone seeking budget-friendly transportation who is comfortable with a car that has some character and needs occasional maintenance.",
      "price": 19500.0,
