    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is a distinguished example of automotive excellence, maintained to rigorous standards. This vehicle exhibits a harmonious balance of performance and aesthetic preservation, offering the discerning driver a sophisticated experience. Its mechanical integrity remains steadfast, complemented by an interior that retains its original character and comfort. We invite you to inspect a vehicle that exemplifies reliable engineering and timeless appeal.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
